       (20190311, '银河英雄传说 Die Neue These 星乱', NULL, 'https://anime-1255705827.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/H3c1460aa4b0e460e9cc377d1034fddfbv.jpg',
        '剧场版',
